{"tid":2453594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑用車內鏡頭收集數據 解放軍下令禁止Tesla 駛入軍事區域","createTime":"2021-03-19T14:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T00:33:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"55b2c7fa6ade83dcd49f1b088e0d150005f431b5","tid":2453594,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕特斯拉近日傳出車內鏡頭會監視車主，外媒消息指出，中國軍方擔心敏感數據被收集，已禁止特斯拉車輛在軍事區域內出現。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》引述知情人士指出，該命令是由中國軍方所發佈，通知特斯拉車主將車輛停在軍方資產以外的地方。該禁令本週傳送至軍人住房，擔心特斯拉正透過車內鏡頭收集敏感數據，且不讓中國政府察覺或控制。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉在中國的代表拒絕評論軍方行動，中國國防部也並未立即回覆《彭博》的傳真置評。<br />\n<br />\n如同通用汽車等其他汽車製造商，特斯拉也在車輛外部裝設小型鏡頭，引導車主進行停車。但大多數的特斯拉models車款還在後視鏡上方裝設1個內鏡頭，用於偵測駕駛的目光所再，包括是否看向道路，或是低頭看腿、戴墨鏡或看向任何地方。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n對於特斯拉是否能檢測到車主？馬斯克本人也在推特回覆 「是的（Yes）」。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3472810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3472810&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=8cee7ece\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3472810&h=af258483\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3472810</a>"},{"pid":"99165cffb8f100f949c97fd08cf1160d6734733f","tid":2453594,"uid":31841,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:28:36.000Z","msg":"teslun係咪唔上得大帽山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df562257286a307c0819195147383a4e2cd201d","tid":2453594,"uid":71508,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"果然係papa Elon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前連登仔誤會咗你奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.