ike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e410c96eb90295781af657311ba5a0b1bc335e6","tid":2453594,"uid":125017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"仲有乜基地比TESLA入得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"Reverse engineering<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6fbf7183abf8b9bb9759bf25c33fd4f33f0e26","tid":2453594,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T22:46:39.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕中國傳出特斯拉車內鏡頭會監視車主一舉一動，引起中共擔憂情資遭美國鎖定，下令禁止軍方、敏感行業的國企和關鍵機構的人員開特斯拉，以免其所收集的數據回傳美國，造成國安資訊外洩。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報導，近日傳出特斯拉的車內鏡頭會監視車主，不斷記錄圖像，並獲得各種數據，例如何時、如何使用以及在何處使用汽車，以及與汽車同步的手機聯絡人列表。知情人士說，中國政府擔心一些數據可能會被送回美國。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士說，中國官員非常關心此事，已經下令禁止軍方、敏感行業的國有企業和關鍵機構的人員駕駛特斯拉汽車，擔心其所收集的數據可能是國家安全漏洞的來源。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3472941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3472941&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=30eed6b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3472941&h=1425bf33\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3472941</a>"},{"pid":"76c65a27db1322a6ec13900ecd8ad32497e994bb","tid":2453594,"uid":183601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T22:52:38.000Z","msg":"乜鄰國其他車無車cam架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"29969319a0b7b96b302a406c97eda1bdfbd33cba","tid":2453594,"uid":287269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32bce47a3ced422359d91eb16228a99b769b96d9","tid":2453594,"uid":55868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"你估你堆大陸電動車咩<i